dmca.title: Defamation Notice DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google

works.description:
They have stolen a flyer from my web page
 
to include it on their blog with defamatory and false information. These  
guys are causing innocent people to get attacked. I took off Peter Sotos  
from the original flyer because he is no longer performing but they  
purposely used the old version to defamate and spread hate. WE Are NO Nazi
 
or have any connection with such politics!!! They should just be arrested 

for what they are doing. I'm consulting a lawyer about this.
